### Knife4j: http://localhost:8080/doc.html

### 创建知识库 - 全参数示例
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/knowledge-bases
Content-Type: application/json

< ../create-kb-body.json

###

### 创建知识库 - 最简（仅 name）
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/knowledge-bases
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "最简测试库"
}

###

### 查询全部知识库
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/knowledge-bases

###

### 按 ID 查询知识库（将 {{kbId}} 替换为创建返回的 id）
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/knowledge-bases?id={{kbId}}

###
